What's new in this update:

• Security: messages between your phone and your PC are now sealed against tampering — an altered or repeated one is rejected.
• Security: your pairing code is now sent only to the PC you picked, never to other devices on your network.
• New: the device card shows how you're connected — LAN, Tailscale, direct or relay.
• Clearer status while connecting.

Important: update the bridge on your PC too.
